# I Built a 7.3‚Ä≥ E-Ink Flight Calendar Using Parts From Amazon

I wake up insanely early most days, and keeping track of duty periods, overnights, and next-day show times gets old fast. I wanted a clean, always-on display that shows:

- Today‚Äôs duty period  
- Tomorrow‚Äôs show time  
- Flight numbers + block times  
- Color-coded ‚Äúon/off duty‚Äù  
- A simple weekly layout  

No tapping through apps.  
No unlocking my phone at 4 AM.  
Just a quiet little display sitting on my desk.

So I built one ‚Äî using **Amazon parts** and a small bit of Python.

---

